episodes.title: Leader of cultlike 'Zizian' group linked to murders in US held without bond in Maryland
episodes.description:
The three people connected to the cultlike group the "Zizians" were caught with several weapons after being found trespassing on the home of a Frostburg, Maryland, resident on Sunday, according to charging documents from Allegany County court.

episodes.title: Leader of cult-like group called "Zizians" arrested in connection to multiple killings in Maryland
episodes.description:
The leader of the so-called "Zizians" - a cultlike group that is connected to a series of violent incidents across the country - has been arrested in Allegany County, Maryland.

Officers apprehended leader Jack Lasota, 34 and Michelle Zajko, 33 for charges of trespassing and possession of a handgun, according to records. However, the circumstances surrounding their arrests remain unclear.

Full story: https://wjla.com/news/nation-world/cult-like-group-linked-to-multiple-killings-and-recent-arrest-in-maryland#
